OL,3,CGirl, 13, to appear in court over
OL,4,Cschool stabbing
OL,6,FA teenage schoolgirl will appear in
OL,7,Fcourt charged with attempted murder
OL,8,Fafter a stabbing at a school in Wales.
OL,10,FPupils at Amman Valley School, also
OL,11,Fknown as Ysgol Dyffryn Aman, in
OL,12,FCarmarthenshire went into lockdown
OL,13,Fjust after 11.20am on Wednesday after
OL,14,Fthe stabbing at the end of morning
OL,15,Fbreak.
OL,17,FTwo teachers and a pupil were hurt in
OL,18,Fthe incident but have since been
OL,19,Freleased from hospital.
