OL,6,F"It is extremely important that there
OL,7,Fshould be no reporting, commentary or
OL,8,Fsharing of information online which
OL,9,Fcould in any way prejudice these
OL,10,Fproceedings."
OL,12,FA 15-year-old boy was arrested later
OL,13,Fon Wednesday after police received
OL,14,Freports about messages on social media
OL,15,Freferring to the stabbing.
OL,17,FOne of the teachers injured in the
OL,18,Fattack has been named as Fiona Elias,
OL,19,Fthe head of year seven.
