OL,3,CGirl, 13, to appear in court over
OL,4,Cschool stabbing
OL,6,FThe second adult is reported to be Liz
OL,7,FHopkin, a special needs teacher.
OL,9,FThe south-west Wales school went into
OL,10,Flockdown after a "code red" alarm
OL,11,Fsounded through the PA system, during
OL,12,Fwhich students and staff are said to
OL,13,Fhave hidden in classrooms ` with one
OL,14,Fpupil reportedly vaulting the school
OL,15,Ffence to get to safety.
